    This class contains constants used by the Simulink model builder. These constants are section and parameter names that refer to the MDL file. Section and parameters are distinguished by the prefix of the constants (SECTION vs PARAM). The remainder of the constant is just like the name in the MDL file. We use mixed case here to express the case differences found in the MDL file, e.g. 'Name' vs 'name'.
